{"type":null,"faqId":49312,"title":"如何调整备忘录的字体大小？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>进入“备忘录”界面，打开选项菜单，然后点击“设置”，即可调整备忘录的字体大小。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188601\" style=\"width:0.50625in;height:0.16875in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>没有专门针对备忘录字体的调整选项。请进入“设置”界面，点击“显示 &gt; 字体大小”，选择合适的字体。此时包括信息、联系人等的字体均会同步调整。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5056","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1447205863000,"seriesProductName":"KIW-AL10,KIW-CL00,KIW-TL00,KIW-TL00H,KIW-UL00","visitedTimes":12,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"调整,备忘录,字体","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}